\c 60
\s Dhavhidhi anochema kukundwa kwavo navavengi vavo
\d Kumutungamiriri wokuimba; nomuimbirwo weShushani Eduti; rwiyo rweMikitami rwaDhavhidhi, kudzidzisa; panguva vaakarwa naAraminaharaimi naAra- mizobha, Joabhu akadzoka
\s akauraya paMupata woMunyu vaE-
\s dhomu vane zviuru zvine gumi nezviviri.
\p
\v 60 Mwari, makatirasha, makatiparadza;
\s Makanga makatsamwa; Haiwa, tidzorei.
\p
\v 2 Makabvundisa nyika; makaitsemura; Gadzirai mitswe yayo; nokuti inozununguka.
\p
\v 3 Makaratidza vanhu venyu zvinhu zvinorema;
\s Makatinwisa waini inobata.
\p
\v 4 Makapa vanokutyai mureza, Kuti uratidzwe nokuda kwezvokwadi.
\p
\v 5 Kuti vadikanwi venyu varwirwe, Tiponesei noruoko rwenyu rworudyi, mutipindure.
\p
\v 6 Mwari akataura pautsvene hwake, achiti, "Ndichafara kwazvo; Ndichaganhura Shekemu,
\s ndichayera mupata weSukoti.
\p
\v 7 Gireadhi ndeyangu Manase ndeyangu;
\s Efuremuwo inhawiro yomusoro wangu;
\s Judha ndiyo tsvimbo yangu youshe.
\p
\v 8 Moabhu ndiwo mudziyo wangu wokushambidzira;
\s Pamusoro peEdhomu ndipo pandichakandira shangu yangu;
\s Iwe Firisitia, pururudza nokuda kwangu."
\p
\v 9 Ndianiko achandiisa muguta rakasimba?
\s Ndianiko achandiperekedza ndiende Edhomu?
